<h2 id="saved-files">Saved Files</h2>
<p>Saved games are by default put in the current directory on some platforms and preset directories on others.</p>

<p>The platforms that have a different default directory are:</p>
<ul>
  <li>OS1</li>
  <li>OS2</li>
</ul>

<p>Read further at Guides/SaveFiles.md</p>
